{"__ud_title":"Application for Software Engineer and PM","__ud_tags":["个人简历","Resume"],"__ud_update_time":1734165876031,"__ud_create_time":1733053419336,"__ud_draft":false,"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":1,"id":"Application-for-Software-Engineer-and-PM"},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Application for Software Engineer and PM"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"个人简介"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"个人简介"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"教育履历"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"教育履历"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"工作履历"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"工作履历"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"项目履历"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"项目履历"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"技能履历"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"技能履历"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"需求"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"需求与价值"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"希望参与有意义有价值的产品、项目。而非关系型项目、骗补贴产品。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"小而美产品，不做大而全。集中一点，登峰造极后再去蔓延。"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"其他"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"其他"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"反感与抵制"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"反感与抵制"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"反感后端上下级官官相护，场景复杂多接口后端不做串接，让前端挨个去调用的（我后端，隔壁组的负责人）。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"反感固守技术资产，与世隔绝万年不革新。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"商场如战场，机会都是瞬息万变。假如什么都等你设计策划评审 商业模式 全成熟了。市场早被别人抢占了。但这并不是脑袋一个闪念就跳过调研、分析、策划设计等阶段，研发直接编码的借口。如何从中找平衡点，甚至计算度量提前捕获机遇，这是决策层、股东、或职业经理人的价值所在。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"抵制恶臭病毒式设计，拼多多砍一刀，凑赞分享，没完没了的开屏广告，首充6元......"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"理想主义的最终幻想"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"理想主义的最终幻想"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"当下最不需要的就是权威,所有的权威及方案都应该经得起证实与证伪。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"方案分歧应以员工投票决策，有职级可以加权重，但不能一言堂。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"一言堂的决策那就绑定事件一人负责到底。杜绝事后甩锅。"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph"}]}